William Edward Phipps https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/William_Edward_Phipps 0 William Edward Phipps (February 4, 1922 – June 1, 2018) was an American actor and producer, sometimes credited simply as William Phipps, perhaps best known for his roles in dozens of classic sci-fi and westerns, both in films and on television.
